{"tid":640483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國遊客凌霄閣墮樓 伏屍山坡","createTime":"2018-04-24T10:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T10:49:21.000Z","uid":41404,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f09acef028121d7f20cf6444ab83a8204a78b3","tid":640483,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"【17:45】據現場消息稱，死者為中國遊客。<br />\n<br />\n山頂凌霄閣發生墮樓事件，下午4時許，一名男子懷疑由上址高處墮下，跌落對開的舊山頂道對上山坡，頭爆肢折當場死亡。警方接報到場，正封鎖現場調查。據現場消息稱，死者為中國遊客。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180424/58112384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F58112384&d=zVjBJXvXBebaGoQd0jZlrZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=2bc54ab1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180424%2F58112384&h=3305cccc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180424/58112384</a>"},{"pid":"cbb99e5f5e8f6a444ae557ddfa09d185f5f57e58","tid":640483,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1f1e758a08a295e82f3f04b74b58fe8366def34","tid":640483,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"啱啱食環架車先黎清走"}]}